- "–ú–æ–ø–µ–¥" means an attack aerial vehicle.

Here are your answer guidelines:
- The first word of your answers must be either "Yes" or "No", depending on the results of your processing.
- You are not allowed to use emojis or symbols. Here are the examples of emojis and symbols: üöÄüî¥‚ö†üí•
